INCLUDES = $(CAKEMLDIR)/developers $(CAKEMLDIR)/misc\
					 $(CAKEMLDIR)/semantics $(CAKEMLDIR)/characteristic\
					 $(CAKEMLDIR)/translator $(CAKEMLDIR)/translator/monadic\
					 $(CAKEMLDIR)/compiler/printing  pure

all: $(DEFAULT_TARGETS) README.md basis_ffi.o
.PHONY: all

README.md: $(CAKEMLDIR)/developers/readme_gen readmePrefix $(wildcard *Script.sml *Lib.sml *Syntax.sml *.lem *.c *.cml */readmePrefix) dependency-order
	$(protect $(CAKEMLDIR)/developers/lint_source) . && $(protect $(CAKEMLDIR)/developers/readme_gen) dependency-order

ifdef POLY
HOLHEAP = $(CAKEMLDIR)/misc/cakeml-heap
endif

EXTRA_CLEANS = basis-heap

ifdef POLY
all: basis-heap

basis-heap: basis.uo
	$(HOLDIR)/bin/hol buildheap -o $@ $<
endif

ifndef CC
CC=gcc
endif
basis_ffi.o: basis_ffi.c
	$(CC) -c $< -o $@
